graph TD
    subgraph Audit Request & Initial Processing
        A[User/AI Assistant] -->|Audit Request| B(MCP Server)
        B --> C(FastAPI Backend)
    end

    subgraph Audit Phases & Data Generation
        C --> P1(Phase 1: Classify AI Risk)
